trans-unit.source: Holds event data for the <xref href="System.Management.ManagementEventWatcher.EventArrived"></xref> event.
The following asynchronous example sets up a WMI timer to raise an event every second, and removes it when no longer needed.
trans-unit.target: I följande exempel för asynkron ställer in en WMI-timer vill utlösa en händelse varje sekund och tar bort den när den inte längre behövs.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Management.ManagementEventWatcher> defines several [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] events which are raised when WMI events are delivered.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Management.ManagementEventWatcher>definierar flera [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] händelser som aktiveras när WMI-händelser levereras.</xref:System.Management.ManagementEventWatcher>

trans-unit.source: Delegates are attached to these events for handling the incoming data.
trans-unit.target: Delegater är kopplade till dessa händelser för att hantera inkommande data.

trans-unit.source: Gets the WMI event that was delivered.
## Property Value The object representing the WMI event.

trans-unit.target: Returnerar en <xref href="System.Management.ManagementBaseObject"> </xref> som innehåller levererade WMI-händelse.
